# Example additions for Raspberry Pi 5 + Waveshare 2-CH CAN HAT (MCP2515, SPI1).
# On Ubuntu 24.04 for Pi, edit: /boot/firmware/config.txt
# On Raspberry Pi OS: /boot/firmware/config.txt
#
# VERIFY oscillator (8 MHz vs 16 MHz) and GPIO interrupts against your HAT revision
# (Waveshare wiki: https://www.waveshare.com/wiki/2-CH_CAN_HAT )

# dtparam=spi=on
# dtoverlay=i2c0
# dtoverlay=spi1-3cs
# dtoverlay=mcp2515,spi1-1,oscillator=16000000,interrupt=22
# dtoverlay=mcp2515,spi1-2,oscillator=16000000,interrupt=13
